sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Discord User
    participant DV as Discord Voice Server
    participant Sub as Node.js Subprocess<br/>(voiceSubprocess.ts)
    participant Main as Bun Main Process<br/>(voiceSessionManager.ts)
    participant LLM as OpenAI Realtime API
    participant ASR as OpenAI ASR<br/>(Transcription WS)

    Note over Main,Sub: Session Start — Parallel Boot
    Main->>Sub: spawn(node --experimental-strip-types)
    Main->>LLM: WebSocket connect (realtime API)
    Sub->>DV: joinVoiceChannel (UDP + WebSocket)
    DV-->>Sub: SessionDescription + DAVE MLS handshake
    Note over Sub: DAVE E2EE: ~10-20s sync native crypto<br/>Event loop blocked
    Sub-->>Main: IPC: { type: "ready" }
    Sub->>Sub: armVoicePlayback("connection_ready")
    Sub-->>Main: IPC: { type: "playback_armed" }
    Main->>Main: Schedule join greeting (3s timer)

    Note over User,ASR: User Speaks
    User->>DV: Opus audio (UDP)
    DV->>Sub: Encrypted Opus packets
    Sub->>Sub: Opus decode → PCM (48kHz stereo)
    Sub->>Sub: Downmix stereo→mono, resample 48k→24k
    Sub-->>Main: IPC: { type: "user_audio", pcmBase64 }
    Main->>ASR: input_audio_buffer.append (base64 PCM)

    Note over Sub: AfterSilence (700ms) or speaking_end
    Sub-->>Main: IPC: { type: "user_audio_end" }
    Main->>ASR: input_audio_buffer.commit
    ASR-->>Main: transcription.completed: "Yo, what's up?"
    Main->>Main: evaluateVoiceReplyDecision()
    Main->>Main: Coalesce window (1100ms)
    Main->>LLM: conversation.item.create + response.create

    Note over Main,Sub: Bot Response Audio
    LLM-->>Main: response.audio.delta (base64 PCM 24kHz)
    Main->>Main: Barge-in suppression check
    Main-->>Sub: IPC: { type: "audio", pcmBase64 }
    Sub->>Sub: drainAudioQueue() — synchronous
    Sub->>Sub: Resample 24k→48k mono→stereo
    Sub->>Sub: PcmJitterBuffer.pushPcm()
    Sub->>Sub: Opus encode (prism-media pipeline)
    Sub->>DV: Opus packet (UDP)
    DV->>User: Voice audio
